metadata.name: Emotional Connection
metadata.description:
Mornings of Mara are blissful, serene, and insanely spiritual.It's a story of my 7-day escape to Masai Mara, known as a quintessential paradise for the world’s finest wildlife that took me to another level of consciousness while keeping me away from the Deserts and Dubai Urban Tech world. I called it as my therapy.

It felt like life gave me a small pause to experience and realize how beautiful mother nature is which can’t be compared or explained in words.

Artist: Kiran Govind 
Camera: Nikon D5 & Nikon 200-400mm F4 
Captured in Dec 2021
Dimensions: 2398 ×1611 
Location: Masai Mara national reserve
Date: 08/09/2022
Edition: 1/1
